Welcome to Amia! We are a persistent world server set in the Forgotten Realms.

You can find our HAK pack on www.amiaworld.com. You need this to enter the server (it also contains the amia_tlk.tlk file the server asks about). Other downloads are optional, but enhance your enjoyment of the game.

Our server portrays Amia, a custom-made popular island far west of the Sword Coast that attracts thrillseekers and opportunists from all over Faerun with the promise of adventure; as well as environs both original and familiar, including the rocky and inhospitable Ruathym, a wintery ancestral dwarven homeland called Barak Runedar, the hoary reaches of the great northern Frozenfar, and the dark underbelly of the Forgotten Realms, the deadly Underdark.

We have a custom deity and prayer system, item crafting system, and job system, with more unique features in the pipeline.

Visit our website for more information: www.amiaworld.com.
